      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH IN VIEW (3) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 30.21 beating Jed's Memory. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can continue on his winning ways. LIGHTNING SPEED (6) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Sandown in a handy 29.52 beating Paw Gordy. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Leading chance again. REMI JOY (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (26.09) in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Solid record here winning two races. Comes through a solid form race last start. Cannot be taken lightly. RIVERS MEET (2) is likely to have admirers.",
